.description
Solar System Wars is a game similar to Space Wars, pitting two players
against each other, in orbit around 0 to 3 stars.  You can choose from 48
different solar systems, or use the random system selector for a different
challenge every round.  A variety of weapons are available.  Supports two
button joysticks but does not require them.  
